=head1 DESCRIPTION

Represents a file upload card. It can optionally receive a C<filename>
and C<fileId> to set a default file. If not received, the user must
provide the file when the Q App runs.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AllowOverride => Bool

A flag indicating if the user can override the default file for the
upload card.


=head2 FileId => Str

The identifier of a pre-uploaded file associated with the card.


=head2 Filename => Str

The default filename to use for the file upload card.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Id => Str

The unique identifier of the file upload card.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Title => Str

The title or label of the file upload card.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Type => Str

The type of the card.



